{
  "texts": [
    "We employ both models as both absolute and relative judges (Section 3).",
    "The judges are implemented using the prompts in Section A, which we borrow from Kim et al. (2024b).",
    "Both prompts ask the model to reason and then output a score.",
    "Embeddings in our judges ϕ(e) are obtained from the base judge's final layer.",
    "The regularization strength γ in the quantitative judges is set by 5-fold cross-validation and we use SGD (Robbins and Monro, 1951) to learn them."
  ]
}